&lt;p&gt;Catawiki is building one of the most dynamic online destinations for exceptional objects. Our Galleries &amp;amp; Art Dealers Market (aka Secondary Market) division is at the heart of this ambition. We are seeking a proven category leader with strong management, commercial, and analytical skills to drive this category forward.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you’ll oversee a diverse international team of experts, ensuring their knowledge and passion for art translate into scalable, data-driven, and high-quality offerings. Your mission is to design and execute a category strategy that delivers measurable growth, grounded in commercial insight, operational excellence, and strong cross-functional collaboration.&amp;nbsp;You will work with Sales, Marketing, Product, and Technology to drive performance, strengthen seller relationships, enhance user experience, while contributing to company-wide initiatives and empowering teams to deliver impact.&lt;/p&gt;
