&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive performance through data:&lt;/strong&gt; Monitor and interpret key metrics (GMV, conversion, lot quality, buyer engagement) and translate insights into clear, actionable improvements across pricing, selection, and operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead and develop a high-performing team:&lt;/strong&gt; Provide clarity, coaching, and accountability to empower experts to deliver at scale and achieve measurable outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Maximise seller relationships and growth:&lt;/strong&gt; Partner with Sales to acquire, negotiate with, and retain high-potential sellers, ensuring a consistent flow of quality supply and strong commercial relationships.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Manage business performance:&lt;/strong&gt; Contribute to category-level P&amp;amp;L, balancing short-term efficiency with long-term strategic growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
