&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;At Catawiki, every day brings the extraordinary! Whether it’s &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.catawiki.com/en/c/583-sports-memorabilia&quot;&gt;Daniel Ricciardo’s Formula 1 Car&lt;/a&gt;, a &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.catawiki.com/en/c/579-fossils&quot;&gt;Woolly Mammoth’s Skeleton&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.catawiki.com/en/l/10035805&quot;&gt;Lady Gaga&#39;s Jumpsuit&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.catawiki.com/en/c/583-sports-memorabilia&quot;&gt;Usain Bolt’s running shoe&lt;/a&gt;, we encounter exceptional objects every day.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re a one-of-a-kind marketplace for buying and selling special objects! Each week we offer over 75,000 unique items in auction&lt;em&gt;,&lt;/em&gt; carefully curated by our passionate in-house experts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Having sold over 20 million unique objects to date, we’re on a mission to become the world’s most popular destination for special objects. As a growing, diverse and sustainable scale-up, we proudly live by our core values:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Taking ownership and driving impact&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Being open to change and feedback&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Being passionate about our mission and our customers.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If these values resonate with you, we’d love to explore how you can join us on this exciting journey!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role and team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an Expert at the Primary Market (Direct from the Artist) team, you will be closely involved with finding and onboarding new artists and screening the artworks from existing artists from Spain and Portugal yet not limited to. You will as well publish auctions weekly. Using your contemporary art expertise and commercial skills, you will be responsible for making artists successful in their development at Catawiki.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Catawiki strives to keep user transactions as transparent and fair as possible, and your honesty and experience play a large part in maintaining this standard; you know better than anyone how exciting and important it is to support artists to sell their works in a dynamic,&amp;nbsp; transparent and trustworthy way.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will find new sources of supply for the markets you will be focusing on and you will work closely with artists in those regions to support them growing their businesses at Catawiki. You will work with other Experts and the Sales team to identify, maximize and align on artists submissions and their sales. You will also be looking for growth opportunities in these markets, through potential partnerships.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Find new supply sources &amp;amp; create Artists leads in Spain and Portugal, in line with our quality guidelines.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Onboarding of Artists through visiting them in their studios or fairs&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Screen (approve or reject) artworks from these markets and support other Experts in their screening when required&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Guide Artists in their performance at Catawiki: whether it is for existing artists to grow or new artists to scale up.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be monitoring performance of the Artists and the markets through dashboards, analysing data on excel sheets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You are an Curator/ Expert in Contemporary Art&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Strong Sales negotiation skills&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Artist management experience&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Strong in analyzing data&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Excellent English communication, and native in Spanish or Portuguese. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Team player and thrive in a diverse team environment&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Great computer skills necessary&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Responsible, good at coordinating and giving operation support&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;It will be highly valued previous experience in auction houses or online platforms.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Where You’ll Be&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role is based in &lt;strong data-start=&quot;148&quot; data-end=&quot;169&quot;&gt;Spain or Portugal&lt;/strong&gt; with a fully remote work-from-home arrangement.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;text text-align-left &quot;&gt;
