&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;At Catawiki, every day brings the extraordinary! Whether it’s &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.catawiki.com/en/c/583-sports-memorabilia&quot;&gt;Daniel Ricciardo’s Formula 1 Car&lt;/a&gt;, a &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.catawiki.com/en/c/579-fossils&quot;&gt;Woolly Mammoth’s Skeleton&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.catawiki.com/en/l/10035805&quot;&gt;Lady Gaga&#39;s Jumpsuit&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.catawiki.com/en/c/583-sports-memorabilia&quot;&gt;Usain Bolt’s running shoe&lt;/a&gt;, we encounter exceptional objects every day.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re a one-of-a-kind marketplace for buying and selling special objects! Each week we offer over 75,000 unique items in auction&lt;em&gt;,&lt;/em&gt; carefully curated by our passionate in-house experts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Having sold over 20 million unique objects to date, we’re on a mission to become the world’s most popular destination for special objects. As a growing, diverse and sustainable scale-up, we proudly live by our core values:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Taking ownership and driving impact&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Being open to change and feedback&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Being passionate about our mission and our customers.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If these values resonate with you, we’d love to explore how you can join us on this exciting journey!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role and team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fuel the Future of Classic Car Sales&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Exceptional cars deserve exceptional treatment&lt;/strong&gt; — and that’s where we come in. At Catawiki, we’re redefining how high-value, collector-grade vehicles are discovered, evaluated, and sold online. We&#39;re a tight-knit, high-performing team of automotive experts based in the Netherlands and Italy, and we’re on the lookout for someone who’s not only passionate about cars but driven by commercial impact. This role is not just about admiring classic cars — it&#39;s about making them move.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Sr. Classic Car Expert, you’ll be working with high-value lots and a targeted, specific buyer audience. We’re obsessed with quality and detail, whether it&#39;s a rare Alfa Romeo or a perfectly preserved Porsche. Each of us brings deep brand knowledge — some of us breathe Italian heritage, others know the German precision scene like the back of their hand. But beyond the passion, we also know what matters most: getting the deal done.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We combine expertise with execution. We help sellers present their cars in the best possible way, but we don’t just &quot;list and hope.&quot; We screen every lot with a commercial lens, we push for promotional and themed auctions, and we ask ourselves: &lt;em&gt;Will this sell? And to whom?&lt;/em&gt; If we don’t have the answer, we ask each other — because we trust our collective knowledge more than any tool. That collaboration fuels our performance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What makes this role exciting?&lt;/strong&gt; You’ll focus on growing the category through new leads from currently unsupported and/or underserved markets and by reactivating dormant sellers. You’ll bring your own network and build trust with new clients, staying sharp on market trends and spotting what’s next before it hits the mainstream. From fairs and local events to one-on-one phone calls, your day will be a mix of deep automotive conversation and smart sales thinking. It’s a dynamic, hybrid environment where autonomy meets teamwork — and if the opportunity arises, we even meet in person to keep the energy high.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What are the challenges?&lt;/strong&gt; We operate in a fast-moving space, and not every lot is a guaranteed success. Our challenge is to build curated auctions that excite buyers, create urgency, and convert. We’re also building bridges between digital and traditional — helping sellers and buyers trust an online auction model for high-value vehicles. That means being responsive, professional, and always ahead of the curve.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In short: we&#39;re car lovers, but even more — we’re deal makers. If you can tell the story behind a car, but also sell it with conviction... if you’re comfortable working with targets and inspired by international growth... if you&#39;re ready to bring your own spark to a strong team — then you might be the one we’re looking for.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Expand Untapped Markets&lt;/strong&gt;: Proactively pursue new leads from unsupported or underserved countries, turning them into active seller portfolios and opening new commercial frontiers for Catawiki’s classic car category.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Revive and Grow Seller Relationships:&lt;/strong&gt; Grow existing seller portfolios and re-engage past sellers by leveraging your automotive expertise, sales instinct, and a personalized approach to relationship management.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Deliver Commercial Results:&lt;/strong&gt; You work confidently with targets and are motivated by outcomes. You leverage your personal network to secure high-value cars and commercial deals that contribute directly to GMV.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Curate High-Quality Auctions&lt;/strong&gt;: You screen incoming lots with care and commercial focus, ensuring auctions are filled with cars that resonate with our buyer audience — both in quality and story.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Create Story-Driven Auctions:&lt;/strong&gt; You bring creativity to the table by proposing themed auctions and promotional lots, using storytelling and strategic thinking to attract new interest and deepen buyer engagement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Support Cross-Category Collaboration:&lt;/strong&gt; While your focus is classic cars, you’re ready to support the motorcycle category when needed — contributing your insight and energy to help the broader automotive team succeed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You are a fluent French or German speaker, and preferably professional level of spoken Dutch.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Network Activator&lt;/strong&gt;: You bring a strong personal network of sellers, collectors, and dealers to Catawiki, expanding our supply of high-quality classic cars and unlocking new commercial opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sales-First Mindset&lt;/strong&gt;: You love beautiful cars, but you know this is a business — you focus on selling, not just showcasing. Your decisions are driven by commercial value, buyer demand, and closing potential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Market Expander&lt;/strong&gt;: You actively grow Catawiki’s footprint in underdeveloped countries and markets, identifying local opportunities, onboarding sellers, and turning gaps into growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Team Energizer&lt;/strong&gt;: You inject fresh perspective and drive into the team, motivating 3 classic car experts and 2 motorcycle experts through collaboration, knowledge sharing, and a passion for performance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Contributor&lt;/strong&gt;: You think beyond listings — identifying untapped segments, proposing structural improvements, and helping shape our approach to classic cars across regions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Automotive Enthusiast with Impact&lt;/strong&gt;: Your passion for cars is matched by your hunger to deliver results. You understand the vehicles, but you also understand what makes them sell — and you act on it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Where You’ll Be&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role is based in France or Germany, with a work-from-home arrangement.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;text text-align-left &quot;&gt;
