&lt;li&gt;Experience in appraising and assessing jewellery;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical skills with the ability to interpret data and make informed decisions;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good grasp of market prices and strong understanding of the various layers needed when curating a lot online;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Extensive trade knowledge with a network of potential sellers and experts in your field;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A real team player with excellent communication and negotiation skills;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in computer tools used for data analysis, reporting and presentations For example Excel or Google Sheets and PowerPoint or Google Slides.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The diplomatic competence needed to act as a mediator in disputes between users;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluent English language skills; French is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
