&lt;p&gt;The role is based in Japan with a fully remote work-from-home arrangement. You will be part of the Luxury Department and will be working closely on our Japan market.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;text text-align-left &quot;&gt;
