&lt;p&gt;This role can be worked remotely across a variety of countries such as Italy, France, Germany or the Netherlands.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;text text-align-left &quot;&gt;
