&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a &lt;strong&gt;commercially driven, entrepreneurial mindset expert&lt;/strong&gt; in our constantly growing World Coins segment who thrives in spotting opportunities, acting fast on market trends, and driving growth. You will play a key role in our continuous path in building high-performing auctions that meet sales targets and exceed expectations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you will:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
