&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build seller relationships&lt;/strong&gt;: Engage your network of dealers, collectors, and traders while proactively onboarding new sellers and strengthening relationships with existing ones.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborate to grow&lt;/strong&gt;: Work closely with Sales and Marketing to align strategies, scale sellers, and achieve ambitious commercial goals.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Leverage data&lt;/strong&gt;: Analyze sales performance and apply insights to optimize pricing, submissions, and auction curation.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is not just about expertise in coins – it’s about &lt;strong&gt;being a high-energy, commercially sharp professional&lt;/strong&gt; who sees opportunities and acts decisively to deliver growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
