&lt;li&gt;You are &lt;strong&gt;entrepreneurial and commercially minded&lt;/strong&gt;, you participate fairs and you have proven experience in buying and selling&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have a &lt;strong&gt;growth mindset&lt;/strong&gt;, you know the market of these coins very well and you are constantly scanning the market for trends, opportunities, and price dynamics.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are &lt;strong&gt;results-oriented&lt;/strong&gt; and thrive on achieving ambitious sales and revenue targets.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have a strong &lt;strong&gt;network of dealers, collectors, and sellers&lt;/strong&gt; and know how to leverage it.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You understand how to &lt;strong&gt;balance independence with structure&lt;/strong&gt;: you bring high energy and initiative while working within organizational goals and frameworks.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are an excellent communicator, fluent in English, and able to act diplomatically when needed.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have experience using &lt;strong&gt;data to drive decisions&lt;/strong&gt; and scale growth.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
