&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead and Inspire a High-Performing Creative Team:&lt;/strong&gt; Manage, mentor, and grow a cross-functional team of designers, copywriters, and creative operations. Foster a strong internal culture while collaborating with external partners to scale quality creative output.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build and Evolve the Catawiki Brand:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Own and elevate our brand identity — visual, verbal, and strategic — ensuring consistency and quality across all touchpoints. Define brand guidelines and apply them rigorously across teams, formats, and markets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Deliver 360° Campaigns That Drive Growth:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Develop and execute integrated campaigns across CRM, Performance, Social, PR, and beyond. Work closely with internal stakeholders to ensure every creative asset delivers business impact and reinforces brand equity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Translate Strategy into Creative That Performs:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Turn complex business objectives and customer insights into compelling creative that cuts through. Ruthlessly prioritize work that drives brand awareness, engagement, and measurable ROI.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Champion Innovation and Scalable Creative Excellence:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Continuously raise the creative bar by exploring new formats, technologies, and tools — with a big emphasis on AI-driven tools — to accelerate production, improve relevance, and stay ahead of industry trends.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Head of Creative will report to the Director of Brand &amp;amp; Communications.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
