&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Proven Creative Leader:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;You bring 8+ years of experience leading multidisciplinary creative teams in fast-paced environments. You’ve thrived in lean, high-growth settings where budgets are limited and creative needs to deliver real business impact — ideally with a mix of in-house and agency experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Brand Thinker: &lt;/strong&gt;You understand how to build, grow, and protect a brand — balancing long-term equity with short-term performance needs across multiple markets, audiences, and touchpoints.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Commercially Minded: &lt;/strong&gt;You connect creative work to business outcomes, using data, insights, and KPIs to prioritize high-impact initiatives. You focus on ROI, not just reach, and know how to make creative highly impactful and deliver our business objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;360° Campaign Builder: &lt;/strong&gt;You have a strong track record of developing integrated campaigns that span CRM, social, performance, PR, and product surfaces — and know how to adapt and scale ideas across each while maintaining coherence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Craft-Obsessed and Quality-Driven: &lt;/strong&gt;You set a high bar for design, copy, and execution. You know how to scale quality without compromising creativity, and you care deeply about every detail — from concept to final output.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI-Powered and Tech-Smart: &lt;/strong&gt;You go beyond curiosity — you&#39;re hands-on with AI tools for design, copy, and motion, and use them to increase speed, efficiency, and quality. You lead by example in bringing innovation into the team’s daily work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborative and Influential: &lt;/strong&gt;You thrive in cross-functional environments, building alignment and trust with marketing, product, brand, and leadership stakeholders. You know how to rally teams around creative ideas that serve broader goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Resilient and Resourceful: &lt;/strong&gt;You’re comfortable navigating ambiguity, shifting priorities, and limited resources. You move fast, make smart calls, and maintain creative integrity — even when the pressure’s on.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
