&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interested?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Apply directly with an English CV and cover letter by submitting your information at the bottom of this page. By submitting your application you agree to &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.catawiki.com/conditions/applicant-privacy-policy.pdf&quot;&gt;Catawiki’s Applicant Privacy Policy&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;If you’re excited about this role but your past experience doesn’t align perfectly with every qualification in the job description, we encourage you to apply anyway. You may be just the right candidate for this or other roles.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;At Catawiki, every day brings the extraordinary! Whether it’s &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.catawiki.com/en/c/583-sports-memorabilia&quot;&gt;Daniel Ricciardo’s Formula 1 Car&lt;/a&gt;, a &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.catawiki.com/en/c/579-fossils&quot;&gt;Woolly Mammoth’s Skeleton&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.catawiki.com/en/l/10035805&quot;&gt;Lady Gaga&#39;s Jumpsuit&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.catawiki.com/en/c/583-sports-memorabilia&quot;&gt;Usain Bolt’s running shoe&lt;/a&gt;, we encounter exceptional objects every day.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re a one-of-a-kind marketplace for buying and selling special objects! Each week we offer over 75,000 unique items in auction&lt;em&gt;,&lt;/em&gt; carefully curated by our passionate in-house experts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Having sold over 20 million unique objects to date, we’re on a mission to become the world’s most popular destination for special objects. As a growing, diverse and sustainable scale-up, we proudly live by our core values:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Taking ownership and driving impact&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Being open to change and feedback&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Being passionate about our mission and our customers.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If these values resonate with you, we’d love to explore how you can join us on this exciting journey!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an IT Automation &amp;amp; Integration Engineer in the IT Systems &amp;amp; Services (ITSS) team, you will play a key role in driving scalable, secure, and intelligent automation across Catawiki’s internal systems. Your mission is to reduce manual work, enhance data and process consistency, and enable seamless cross-system experiences through well-designed, resilient integrations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll build smart, reusable automation workflows using both cloud-native infrastructure and modern Integration-Platform-as-a-Service (iPaaS) solutions such as Okta Workflows, and GCP Application Integration. Working closely with stakeholders across IT, People, and Finance, you’ll translate business needs into system integrations that are efficient, secure, and built to scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a hands-on engineering role involving scripting (Python, shell script, etc), cloud orchestrations, API integrations, Slack bot development, and the incorporation of AI capabilities through LLMs like OpenAI, etc.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Design &amp;amp; Implement Automation Workflows&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Develop and maintain automations across platforms like Okta, Jamf, Jira, Slack, HiBob, Workday, and Google Workspace using both custom code and iPaaS tools.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build and Manage System Integrations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Architect and deploy system integrations using REST APIs, Webhooks, and OpenAPI specifications, ensuring reliable and secure data flows across internal platforms.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Leverage iPaaS Platforms&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Use iPaaS tools such as Okta Workflow or N8N, and Workato to accelerate integration delivery, manage low-code/no-code connectors, and support event-driven workflows.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Develop Slack Bots&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; Build scalable and secure Slack bots that connect to internal tools for automated actions, workflows, and notifications using Slack APIs.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Use GCP for Backend Logic&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; Implement cloud-based automation with GCP services like Cloud Functions for processing, orchestration, and data handling.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Infuse AI &amp;amp; LLM Capabilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; Incorporate AI-driven logic using OpenAI to enhance workflows, enable intelligent decision-making, and support natural language processing.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborate &amp;amp; Document&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; Translate business needs into technical requirements; maintain clear documentation of architecture, data mappings, automation workflows, and API logic.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Monitor, Optimize &amp;amp; Secure&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; Monitor system health and workflow execution, troubleshoot integration issues, and enforce compliance with privacy and InfoSec standards.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll bring:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience &amp;amp; Background&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of experience in IT automation, system integration, or infrastructure engineering.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Direct experience working with or managing iPaaS platforms such as Okta Workflow,&amp;nbsp; N8N, Workato, Tray.io, Boomi, Zapier, or MuleSoft.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Skills&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficient in Python, shell script or any other programming languages for automation and scripting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid understanding of REST APIs, SOAP, Webhooks, OAuth2, JSON/XML.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with system integrations for tools like HiBob, Workday, Okta, Jamf, Workday, Google Workspace, and Jira.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cloud &amp;amp; Platform Knowledge&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience with Google Cloud Platform (Cloud Functions). Deep knowledge of Slack APIs and building internal bots for team workflows.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI Integration Awareness&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience or familiarity integrating LLMs and AI services, including OpenAI, into automation pipelines.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operational &amp;amp; Interpersonal Strengths&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical and debugging skills for complex, multi-system environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to design integrations with security, observability, and scalability in mind.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable working cross-functionally with both technical and business teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
