&lt;p&gt;At Catawiki, we connect millions of enthusiasts with exceptional objects – from dinosaur skeletons to luxury watches and cultural treasures. As Europe’s fastest-growing online auction platform, we combine startup energy with scale-up ambition.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a Senior Legal &amp;amp; Compliance Counsel who thrives at the intersection of business and regulation. This is a unique opportunity to shape commercial deals and compliance strategy in one of Europe’s most exciting marketplaces.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive commercial growth &lt;/strong&gt;– draft, review, and negotiate impactful agreements across SaaS, strategic partnerships, procurement, international expansion, and platform operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Shape compliance strategy&lt;/strong&gt; – design and evolve frameworks covering consumer law, AML &amp;amp; sanctions, Digital Services Act, cultural property, product safety, and other platform obligations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cut through complexity&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;– distill complex legal and regulatory questions into clear business choices, aligned with Catawiki’s risk appetite.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Be a trusted business partner&lt;/strong&gt; – provide pragmatic, risk-based guidance to product, tech, marketing, and commercial teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Structure and lead projects&lt;/strong&gt; – oversee regulatory rollouts, new market entries, and cross-border deals from start to finish, ensuring effective delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strengthen the function for scalable impact&lt;/strong&gt; – design smart processes, playbooks, templates, and training that embed legal and compliance awareness into everyday decision-making, ensuring the function scales with the business.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mentor and coach –&lt;/strong&gt; support junior counsels, empowering them to grow into broader responsibilities across commercial and compliance topics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
