&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A qualified EU lawyer with 8+ years’ experience spanning commercial law and compliance, ideally in e-commerce, tech, or platform businesses.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to negotiate cross-border agreements and navigate complex, international regulatory landscapes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experienced in balancing legal accuracy with commercial pragmatism, applying a risk-based approach.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Confident in advising on both contracts and compliance frameworks (SaaS, vendor, and marketplace agreements; AML, sanctions, consumer law, DSA, product regulation).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A strong communicator who can influence and align stakeholders at every level – from engineers, commercial teams to executives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong project management skills and comfort working in matrixed, cross-functional teams&lt;/li&gt;
