&lt;p&gt;If these values resonate with you, we’d love to explore how you can join us on this exciting journey!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a passionate and talented Senior UX Researcher to join our UX team. This is a pivotal role that combines hands-on research expertise with leadership in maturing our research practice. You will take a mixed-methods approach, leveraging both qualitative and quantitative insights, to deeply understand the needs, behaviours, and motivations of our users. Additionally, you will champion customer-centricity, democratize research through tools and best practices, and own the systematic measurement of customer satisfaction across the user journey.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead Research Initiatives&lt;/strong&gt;: Set the research strategy and research roadmap for Catawiki. Design and execute research activities that drive a deep understanding of our customer base and influence the most important product decisions.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Empower Teams&lt;/strong&gt;: Collaborate with cross-functional teams, including designers, product managers, and developers, to democratize research. Provide teams with the tools, methods, and best practices needed to conduct their own research.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mixed-Methods Approach&lt;/strong&gt;: Design and conduct foundational, formative, and evaluative research by combining qualitative methods (e.g., moderated/unmoderated usability testing, focus groups, interviews, card sorting) with quantitative techniques (e.g., surveys, A/B testing, behavioral analytics, and statistical analysis) to create a holistic view of user behavior. Use tools like Maze, AB Smartly, Mixpanel, and Hotjar to gather insights.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Advocate for Users&lt;/strong&gt;: Act as a vocal advocate for customer-centricity, ensuring the user perspective informs decision-making at every level. Influence stakeholders by delivering impactful and actionable research findings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Measure and Improve Customer Satisfaction&lt;/strong&gt;: Own and systematically measure customer satisfaction across the user journey. Define success metrics and partner with data experts to track and analyze these metrics to inform the roadmap.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Communicate Insights&lt;/strong&gt;: Present findings in compelling and innovative ways, tailoring communication to resonate with diverse stakeholders. Create user models, personas, and other tools to ensure insights stick with teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Foster Research Maturity&lt;/strong&gt;: Develop and implement a UX research roadmap that aligns with organizational goals. Mentor team members and champion a culture of curiosity and continuous learning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We’re Looking For:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Proven Track Record&lt;/strong&gt;: 4+ years of experience in UX research with a demonstrable history of improving products and services through research.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Quantitative and Qualitative Balance&lt;/strong&gt;: Ability to combine qualitative and quantitative insights to paint a comprehensive picture of user behaviors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Customer Advocacy&lt;/strong&gt;: Passion for customer-centricity and a proven ability to champion the user perspective within an organization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaboration&lt;/strong&gt;: Experience working closely with cross-functional teams in agile environments, including designers, product managers, engineers, and data experts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Communication Skills&lt;/strong&gt;: Exceptional storytelling and communication skills to effectively “sell” research insights and influence decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Organizational Skills&lt;/strong&gt;: Highly organized with an entrepreneurial mindset and a proactive approach to identifying opportunities and solving challenges. Comfortable working with tight deadlines. &lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Education&lt;/strong&gt;: Bachelor’s degree in Human Factors, Human-Computer Interaction, Psychology, Sociology, or a related field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;text text-align-left &quot;&gt;
